                <h1 class="title">Anna <span class="text-gradient">Chumakova</span><br>
            <span class="tagline block">SEO SERVICES</span> <span class="tagline block">//</span> <span class="tagline block">WEB MASTER</span>
            </h1>
        
            <p class="hero-description">
                The Mako is the fastest shark in the ocean. And I’m telling you: Be Mako.
            </p>
            <p>
                While you are second-guessing whether your website even needs SEO, your competitors are already stealing your clients. 
                In modern search, victory belongs to those who act with precision, aggression, and superior tech. 
                <!-- This website is a living proof of next-gen SEO in action. 
                I architect search infrastructure at the intersection of automation, AI, and flawless code to give your business a permanent competitive advantage. -->
            </p>
            <a href="#contact" class="mako-btn code-accent">
            <span>GET IN TOUCH</span>
            <span class="btn-glow"></span>
            </a>
            </div>
             
        </section>
        <section class="page-content"><About /></section>
        <section class="page-content"><Work /></section>
        <section class="page-content"><Services /></section>
        <section class="page-content"><Contact /></section>

    </div> 
</Layout>

